

DuoTerm is a terminal use for debugging serial applications.
It is written in Python and is open-source.

Requirements to run the app from source:
  * Have Python 3 installed. (3.6) for best results.
  * Install pygame module with the command:
    pip install pygame
  * Install the serial module:
    pip install serial


To run DuoTerm you just need to run the DuoTerm.py file as you would with any other python script.

DuoTerm is only compatible with Windows.

Changes are welcome. (Pull-requests)
